    "description": "Are you a skilled Senior Doctor looking for your next big career move? Metropolis Healthcare in Patna offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Metropolis Healthcare:\nMetropolis Healthcare is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Administer medications and treatments as prescribed\n• Maintain sterile environments and follow infection control protocols\n• Maintain accurate clinical documentation in electronic health records\n• Respond to medical emergencies and provide immediate care\n• Participate in quality improvement initiatives and clinical audits\n• Ensure patient privacy and maintain confidentiality\n• Conduct routine health assessments and screenings\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in CPT Codes\n• Proficiency in Infection Control\n• Proficiency in Medical Terminology\n• Proficiency in EMR/EHR\n• Proficiency in Surgical Procedures\n• Proficiency in BLS/ACLS\n• Proficiency in Clinical Research\n• Proficiency in Telemedicine\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Patna, Bihar, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Metropolis Healthcare!",
